data.name: lblFirstTime.Text
data.value:
PLEASE READ!
- yt-dlp is REQUIRED for this application to work. Download it via the link in blue on the bottom.
- VLC Media Player is highly recommended; some videos export as .webm which VLC handles without a problem.
- Recoding (toggle before downloading) lets you export with another extension; it takes a long time and requires a lot of GPU power, use with caution.
